they were no longer cold.

03:29.326 --> 03:30.451
<i>♫ Sleep in heavenly peace ♫</i>
- Which is why

03:30.452 --> 03:31.578
many believe today

03:31.579 --> 03:34.581
that when the moon is
full on Christmas Eve,

03:34.582 --> 03:37.381
it offers a magical time of peace,

03:38.252 --> 03:40.587
a blessing on the world.

03:40.588 --> 03:42.932
<i>♫ Holy night ♫</i>

03:44.175 --> 03:45.592
<i>♫ Shepherds quake ♫</i>

03:45.593 --> 03:49.314
